---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Store Rewards Programs Guide">
  <!-- Featured Image Section -->
  <div class="relative h-[300px] sm:h-[400px] overflow-hidden">
    <img 
      src="/images/rewards/store-rewards-hero.webp" 
      alt="Store Rewards Programs and Loyalty Cards"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/50 to-black/20 flex items-center justify-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white text-center max-w-4xl px-4">
        Maximize Your Savings with Store Rewards Programs
      </h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Understanding Store Loyalty Programs</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Store loyalty programs are free to join and offer various benefits including points, cash back, and exclusive discounts.
        Learn how to make the most of these programs to multiply your savings.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Key Benefits:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Earn points on every purchase that can be redeemed for store credit or merchandise</li>
          <li>Access to member-only sales and exclusive discounts</li>
          <li>Special birthday rewards and seasonal bonuses</li>
          <li>Digital coupons loaded directly to your loyalty card</li>
          <li>Early access to sales and promotions</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Popular Store Rewards Programs</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="border-b pb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">CVS ExtraCare</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Earn 2% back in ExtraBucks rewards on most purchases, plus receive personalized deals and pharmacy rewards.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Quarterly ExtraBucks rewards</li>
            <li>Weekly personalized deals</li>
            <li>Pharmacy rewards program</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b pb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Walgreens Balance Rewards</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Earn points on purchases and pharmacy services, plus receive exclusive member pricing.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Points on every purchase</li>
            <li>Bonus points on featured items</li>
            <li>Cash rewards redemption</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b pb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Target Circle</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Earn 1% rewards on every purchase, plus get access to hundreds of deals and personalized offers.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>1% earnings on every purchase</li>
            <li>Birthday reward</li>
            <li>Community giving program</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Tips for Maximizing Rewards</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-primary/5 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-4">
          <li>
            <strong>Join Multiple Programs:</strong>
            <p class="mt-2">Sign up for rewards programs at all stores you frequently shop at. Most are free to join.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Stack Rewards with Coupons:</strong>
            <p class="mt-2">Combine store rewards with manufacturer coupons and store sales for maximum savings.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Track Points and Expiration Dates:</strong>
            <p class="mt-2">Keep track of when your rewards expire and use them before they're lost.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Use Store Apps:</strong>
            <p class="mt-2">Download store apps to easily track rewards and access digital coupons.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Time Your Purchases:</strong>
            <p class="mt-2">Plan big purchases during bonus points events or special promotions.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-8">
        <li>Letting rewards expire without using them</li>
        <li>Not checking for bonus point opportunities</li>
        <li>Forgetting to link your loyalty card to your account</li>
        <li>Missing out on special promotions and events</li>
        <li>Not combining rewards with other savings opportunities</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Ready to Start Saving?</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Begin by signing up for rewards programs at your most frequently visited stores. Download their apps,
          and start tracking your rewards. Remember to check for special promotions and bonus point opportunities
          regularly.
        </p>
        <p>
          For more savings tips and strategies, explore our other resources or sign up for our newsletter to stay
          updated on the latest deals and rewards program updates.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
